text: Jean-Sébastien Vialatte (born 30 January 1951) is a French politician and Mayor of Six-Fours-les-Plages. From 2002 to 2017 he was a member of the National Assembly of France, where he represented the Var department. Vialatte is a member of the Les Republicains. ==References== Category:1951 births Category:Living people Category:Union for a Popular Movement politicians Category:Deputies of the 12th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Deputies of the 13th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Deputies of the 14th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic
